values: anyone read this? ... i dont want to live here anymore... i dont even know if this is even still running. im moving to detroit or vermont :) i miss someone and i think its time that i go get her:)

man.. i cant wait till these next weeks coming up. they are going to be one of the best. going back home should be fun. i miss mom and dad 2:) they are the best. as for the presents.. haha rent sucks. all those peeps that pay rent know what im talking about. no money left for anything. makes me sad... that brings me to my next thing.. why is everyone always sad?? i havent grasped that concept yet. it seems like everyone is in this slump or something.. but ill be the guy that brings them out of it. i really hate seeing people upset. i mean its ok to be upset for a lil but to hold onto something is such a waste. thats when it really starts draging you down. i mean i could go on and on why i should be sad as heck but i got so much to live for and the things that happen in my life between these years means very little in the big picture. if something is bothering you talk to someone about it.. they might have gone through that same thing. people are like that. if someone is hurting you.. let them go!! not worth it, at all. ah.. well there. hope everyone is staying warm. peace

hmm strange. i feel strange. but good. its a good strange. its like a happy but at the same time lonely thing... i dont know can anyone know what im talking about? alright thats cool. i miss things.. like i havent had those things before but i miss them. but i dont know what thos things are, well i do, well some. im rambling... sorry. but wait its my thoughts so im all good. its kinda weird posting my thoughts so everyone can read... i hope people dont think im doing this for attention. im not.. i dont think anyone will read this but if they do , hey thats fun. megan.. i know youll probably read this:) ive already said it but i miss you so much. you know weve known each other for like 3 years.. well i knew of you on the bus, bus 7 yeaaa, good times. so its more like 4 years for me but hey. ill be home soon. .... this concludes my journal
first time doing this, hope this works... and im cold
